{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"a2017a36-32d8-4b19-8d2e-0aea2532e323","content":"Yes, you will run into compatibility issues. **MSTest v3 requires .NET 6.0 or later** (or .NET Framework 4.6.2+), so:\n\n| Target Framework | Compatible with MSTest v3? |\n|---|---|\n| `net462` | ✅ Yes |\n| `netcoreapp3.1` | ❌ No — dropped in MSTest v3 |\n| `net5.0` | ❌ No — dropped in MSTest v3 |\n\n**To migrate**, you'd need to:\n1. Replace `netcoreapp3.1` and `net5.0` with `net6.0` or later (e.g., `net8.0`).\n2. Update MSTest packages to v3 (`3.x`).\n\nIf you still need to test against those older TFMs, you'll have to stay on MSTest v2 for those targets or split the project.\n\nWould you like me to update the project file for MSTest v3?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"d88c497b-a4ab-4881-9658-a6779312440a","outputTokens":237,"requestId":"23C3:9FE27:47AB3A:4CD402:6A03112F"},"id":"22108029-bafa-4e36-bcf1-1cbf62fcc49a","timestamp":"2026-05-12T11:38:31.404Z","parentId":"1504b9fb-5868-4055-b368-f5401e0abc47"}
